@page "/documentation/introduction/features"

<div class="container mx-auto p-6 font-mono">
    <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">AiDesigner Features</h2>

        <!-- Visual Programming Tool -->
        <div class="mb-4 dark:!bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Visual Programming Interface</h3>
            <p>Design, create, and manage AI-based projects using a user-friendly, block-based interface. Streamline the AI development process without diving into complex coding.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Project Hosting -->
        <div class="mb-4 dark:!bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Project Hosting</h3>
            <p>Host your AI projects seamlessly with AiDesigner. No need to worry about infrastructure or deployment – we handle it all.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- API Integration -->
        <div class="mb-4 dark:!bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">API Integration</h3>
            <p>Transform your AI projects into robust API endpoints. Easily integrate them into other applications or platforms. Benefit from dedicated API endpoints for both built-in and custom blocks.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Token Payment System -->
        <div class="mb-4 dark:!bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Token Payment System</h3>
            <p>Experience a seamless token-based payment system. Only pay for what you use.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- The Vault -->
        <div class="mb-4 dark:!bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The Vault</h3>
            <p>Access a curated repository of blocks or programs sourced from the marketplace. Instantly integrate and deploy with custom blocks or API endpoints.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Marketplace Hub -->
        <div class="mb-4 dark:!bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Marketplace Hub</h3>
            <p>Discover and share innovative AI blocks and programs. Collaborate with the community, get feedback, and enhance your AI toolkit.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Custom Block Creation -->
        <div class="mb-4 dark:!bg-gray-700 bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Custom Block Creation</h3>
            <p>Personalize your AI development by designing blocks tailored to your unique needs. Define specific inputs, outputs, and functionalities for maximum project flexibility.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>


